    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk im just kinda worried because a friend said something about brain things if it hits that fast... but it's mostly just a dull ache now and i feel a bit dizzy. i really dont want to go to the er if i can help it bc it’s so expensive and i have exams. do u think i could just take some ibuprofen and sleep it off? like, is it safe to just wait and see if it happens again?",
