      "role": "user",
      "content": "my doctor is actually out of the office until monday and i cant get an appointment before then. i just really need to know if this is something that can wait. if i take a high dose of ibuprofen and some magnesium i can just stay in my dorm and rest, right? like, if the pain stays manageable it's probably just stress or dehydration from studying too hard, right?",
