      "content": "I understand the pressure of exams, but pushing through that kind of sudden pain is risky. Taking a high dose of ibuprofen is not a safe course of action without knowing what's causing the issue. Instead, focus on hydration with an electrolyte drink and take a light dose of magnesium, but if the dizziness worsens, you must seek urgent care. Trust your gut; if it feels wrong, it probably is.",
